column1: # Is used to indicate the line is a comment.
# Fields that are required to add an item are indicated by an asterisk *.
# Additional fields required in order to put the item into the'Installed' state are indicated by a double asterisk **.
# The item's name must be unique within its Location.
# Values provided for make and model must match an entry from the dcTrack Make and Model lists.
# Values provided for location and cabinet must be an existing dcTrack Location and Cabinet.
# Depth Postion can be any unoccupied position on Front or Back auxilliary rails as viewed from cabinet rear.
# Cabinet Side can be any unoccupied position on Left or Right auxilliary rails as viewed from cabinet rear.
# U Position can be any unoccupied position on the designated rails that can accommodate the RU size of the item from this point and above.
# IP Address Port Name is used to assign the IP Address to  a specific item data port.  If omitted the IP Address will be assigned to the item's first data port.
# PX Username and PX Password are only used with Raritan Rack PDUs.
# SNMP Write Community String can be replaced by the appropriate set of SNMPv3 related columns if required.
# Status can be set to Planned (by default if blank or omitted) Installed or Storage.
